            <br>
            <span class="style8"><span class="style7">Welcome to Pelma Inc.</span></span>            <br>
            <br>
  Pelma Inc. has been a leader in corporate finance since 1983. It has consulted with industrial corporations and commercial ventures of all sizes and types. Its scope of expertise consists in assisting top level managers with their financial projects, transactions and valuations. Pelma Inc. has  expertise in the purchase and sale of companies, project analysis, selling of business units or minority positions and   financing. We work extensively with Oracle's Hyperion Strategic Finance software, which supplements our analysis of your specific situation. </p>
